Package: multiomeKO
Type: Package
Title: Interpretable Two-Stage Virtual KO for Paired scRNA+scATAC (Multiome)
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: c(
  person(given = "OpenAI", family = "Assistant", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "noreply@example.com")
)
Description: Implements a biologically constrained two-stage model (Regulator->ATAC->RNA)
    for paired single-cell multiome (scRNA+scATAC) data represented as Seurat/Signac objects.
    Supports virtual knock-out (counterfactual) prediction producing delta-ATAC and delta-RNA,
    adaptive penalties from motif/link/distance/GWAS fine-mapping, and metacell pseudobulk.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    Matrix,
    glmnet,
    Seurat,
    Signac,
    GenomicRanges,
    IRanges,
    GenomeInfoDb
Suggests:
    rtracklayer
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
